text: Nathalie Marie Andr√©e Baye (born 6 July 1948) is a French actress. She is known for her roles in Every Man for Himself (1980), Strange Affair (1981), La Balance (1982), and The Young Lieutenant (2005). In 2009, she was made a Chevalier of the Legion of Honour. Her other movie roles include Day for Night (1973), Catch Me If You Can (2002), Tell No One (2006) and The Assistant (2015). ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:French movie actors Category:French television actors Category:French stage actors Category:French voice actors
